3851236299573", "tr": 1, "mid": "3873855015956559", "times": 1, "childnum": 1, "t": 1439082471, "totalChildren": 1, "dr": 1, "children": [{"evtlist": [1713], "uid": "2393802281", "dep": 0, "text": "“失当”", "pid": "3873855015956559", "tr": 0, "mid": "3873861852201777", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1439084101, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "刑天不死"}], "name": "刑天不死"}, {"evtlist": [1713], "uid": "1821054801", "dep": 0, "text": "司马南特别爱转一些小马甲号的吹捧帖，这是为什么？[思考]", "pid": "3873851236299573", "tr": 0, "mid": "3873855204395772", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1439082516, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "自降魔"}, {"evtlist": [1713], "uid": "1894385102", "dep": 0, "text": "祝华新，黑白颠倒，是非不分！", "pid": "3873851236299573", "tr": 0, "mid": "3873855241724041", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1439082525, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "历史是个小大叔"}, {"evtlist": [1713], "uid": "1765443874", "dep": 0, "text": "被众人骂其实就是报应呗。老毛活着沒人敢骂，死了快四十年还有那么多人骂，只因当初大权在握。你沒死就有那么多人骂，只因你没权呗，当然你死了就不会有人骂了。", "pid": "3873851236299573", "tr": 0, "mid": "3873855854526220", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1439082671, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "虎儿爷tiger"}, {"evtlist": [1713], "uid": "1693719801", "dep": 0, "text": "看来司马南好像比曰本鬼子还可恨，这么咬牙切齿说安培就好了。", "pid": "3873851236299573", "tr": 0, "mid": "3873859532607960", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1439083546, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "闲言傻人"}, {"evtlist": [1713], "uid": "2303457333", "dep": 0, "text": "与司马大哥有杀父之仇？还是夺妻之恨？如此血海深仇！", "pid": "3873851236299573", "tr": 1, "mid": "3873859809377080", "times": 1, "childnum": 1, "t": 1439083614, "totalChildren": 1, "dr": 1, "children": [{"evtlist": [1713], "uid": "2161679310", "dep": 0, "text": "不能任由网上暴力、恐怖主义横行 ", "pid": "3873859809377080", "tr": 0, "mid": "3873864267936610", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1439084677, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "华老太"}], "name": "齐翁在越"}, {"evtlist": [1713], "uid": "2155480694", "dep": 0, "text": "这些人渣什么都有可能干出来，文登就是一例，不能轻视，没报警吗？报警没受理吗？警察没调查处理吗？等结果。", "pid": "3873851236299573", "tr": 0, "mid": "3873859935815954", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1439083643, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "日出前的时刻"}, {"evtlist": [1713], "uid": "2028551547", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3873851236299573", "tr": 0, "mid": "3873861655144781", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1439084054, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "精密探险"}, {"evtlist": [1713], "uid": "1612231631", "dep": 0, "text": "语言暴力比街头斗殴更具杀伤力 ", "pid": "3873851236299573", "tr": 0, "mid": "3873861994585163", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1439084135, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "夕夕心田"}, {"evtlist": [1713], "uid": "2753938231", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3873851236299573", "tr": 0, "mid": "3873863316596681", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1439084450, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "爱心无价_47041"}, {"evtlist": [1713], "uid": "3938325704", "dep": 0, "text": "司马南为什么不好好反省，为什么有这么多人对你恨之入骨？其实你正是利用了这点，以极低的付出，获得了极大的利润。你不过就是一个只看利润，狗吃良心的奸商。 ", "pid": "3873851236299573", "tr": 0, "mid": "3873863533859356", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1439084502, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "科林斯2013"}, {"evtlist": [1713], "uid": "2012881387", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3873851236299573", "tr": 0, "mid": "3873864238553798", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1439084670, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "ggy508"}, {"evtlist": [1713], "uid": "1458707405", "dep": 0, "text": "", "pid": "3873851236299573", "tr": 0, "mid": "3873865287741009", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t": 1439084920, "totalChildren": 0, "dr": 0, "children": [], "name": "谢耳朵的听网之耳"}, {"evtlist": [1713], "uid": "1663003935", "dep": 0, "text": "我很少关注司马的，但是小崔经常提，所以我开始关注了。一段时间了，觉得司马除了书法不错，言词也很温和啊。为何招来那么多偏激的攻击呢？政治我不懂，但一个人言行，应该是修养的体现吧。 ", "pid": "3873851236299573", "tr": 0, "mid": "3873866760168727", "times": 1, "childnum": 0, "t